title Training time Flow

Email Dataframe->Text Dataframe: Extracion

Text Dataframe->Pre-Processed Data: PreProcessing
Pre-Processed Data->Structured Data: Structuring
Structured Data -> Train Data, Test Data: Train Test Split
Train Data, Test Data-> Tokens: Tokenization
Tokens -> Encoder: glove vectors embedding
Encoder->Decoder: Encoder_outputs, hidden states


loop minimizing the loss/epoch
    Encoder->Decoder: Optimization
end
